T1  - Bold, broad, rigorous, and…relevant? Designing entrepreneurship research for translation
AU  - Waldron, Theodore L.
AU  - McMullen, Jeffery S.
AU  - Newbert, Scott L.
AU  - Payne, G. Tyge
AU  - York, Jeffrey G.
JO  - Journal of Business Venturing
VL  - 40
